data.description: Prepare to fall in love with the incredible potential of this split level home! With over 1,800 sprawling square feet of living space, the opportunities for transformation are simply mind blowing. As you enter, you'll be greeted by a spacious living room that seamlessly flows into the kitchen with a dining area. Upstairs are 3 generously sized bedrooms complete with a full bath. Venture downstairs, you'll find a finished basement boasting a convenient half bath & laundry room. That's not all! An impressive addition awaits as you continue towards the back of the home. This expansive space encompasses a large family room, convenient kitchenette, full bath, laundry room, and an additional bonus room. The possibilities are endless with this added space! Imagine transforming it into a luxurious in-law apartment, providing a private & comfortable living area for extended family or guests. Alternatively, let your imagination run wild & turn it into your very own private master suite. With so much room to play with, the potential for stunning transformations within these walls is truly boundless. Unleash your creativity & envision the home of your dreams coming to life.
